Interface ReminderDatabase.ReminderDatabaseStore

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ReminderDatabase.ReminderArrayStore, ReminderDatabase.ReminderFirebaseStore
    Enclosing class:
    ReminderDatabase

    public static interface ReminderDatabase.ReminderDatabaseStore
    Interface for interacting with ReminderDatabaseStore instances. These instances offer methods for reading and writing Reminder data to various backends, including Firebase (via the ReminderFirebaseStore).
